com.gensym.classes
Class SubscriptionManager

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.gensym.classes.SubscriptionManager
public class SubscriptionManager
extends Object

SubscriptionManager is a class to maintain and manager item subscription process. The class can store subscribed attributes with their itemlistener, and also keep corresponding subscription handles for unsubscribing later.
